<para style="p">A psalm of the sons of Korah; a song.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />On the holy mount stands the city he founded;</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Yahweh loves the gates of Zion</para>

<para style="q1">more than all the tents of Jacob.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Glorious things are said of you, city of God.

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>
